112
00:07:34,560 --> 00:07:35,579
Lin Xia used

113
00:07:35,579 --> 00:07:37,000
to be Jiuyao's CEO.

114
00:07:37,519 --> 00:07:38,120
You two do

115
00:07:38,720 --> 00:07:39,519
have a special bond.

116
00:07:42,120 --> 00:07:42,680
Mr. Luo,

117
00:07:42,819 --> 00:07:43,860
I have urgent business.

118
00:07:44,199 --> 00:07:44,800
I'll get going.

119
00:07:45,040 --> 00:07:45,540
Okay.

120
00:07:56,339 --> 00:07:57,879
