131
00:08:22,860 --> 00:08:24,540
I worked as nightclub DJ,

132
00:08:24,540 --> 00:08:25,420
not hostess.

133
00:08:26,980 --> 00:08:27,639
Moreover,

134
00:08:27,980 --> 00:08:30,620
I studied business management theories

135
00:08:30,620 --> 00:08:31,620
and got the certificates

136
00:08:32,460 --> 00:08:33,740
through hard work.

137
00:08:35,500 --> 00:08:36,039
Everyone,

138
00:08:36,480 --> 00:08:37,139
today

139
00:08:37,399 --> 00:08:39,200
I have another announcement to make.

140
00:08:40,220 --> 00:08:42,580
Ye Dong, Jiuyao Group's

141
00:08:42,940 --> 00:08:43,759
chairman,

142
00:08:44,120 --> 00:08:45,159
has decided

143
00:08:45,519 --> 00:08:47,539
