is a recognition of her business acumen.

157
00:09:17,639 --> 00:09:19,080
I hope Ms. Bai will

158
00:09:19,279 --> 00:09:21,220
contribute to our group's success

159
00:09:21,500 --> 00:09:22,880
and achieve win-win cooperation.

160
00:09:24,519 --> 00:09:25,019
Alright,

161
00:09:25,279 --> 00:09:26,419
today's press conference

162
00:09:26,419 --> 00:09:27,100
